' ============================================================
' Title:     NASIM Application — Wire Log Component Diagram
' Boundary:  NASIM Application (container) — Wire Log Group
' Purpose:   Agent-provider-tool interaction logging, replay, and session forking
'            CSR Layer: Infrastructure
